14:22.016 --> 14:23.550
to be held hostage by.

14:23.551 --> 14:25.819
Again, a deranged gunman comes to mind.

14:25.820 --> 14:27.253
Look,

14:27.254 --> 14:28.488
not my business but...

14:28.489 --> 14:30.490
she's not trying to be on your case.

14:30.491 --> 14:31.725
I think she just wants you to...

14:31.726 --> 14:33.693
find your thing.

14:33.694 --> 14:37.095
Wait, she talks to you about me?

14:37.730 --> 14:39.499
Hi.

14:39.500 --> 14:41.668
I was really worried. I'm so glad

14:41.669 --> 14:42.957
- you are still here.
