14:49.476 --> 14:51.044
Yeah.

14:51.045 --> 14:51.993
- Do me a favor,
- Mm-hmm.

14:51.994 --> 14:53.780
call your dad and your
brother and your sister.

14:53.781 --> 14:55.248
Tell 'em that we're fine...

14:55.249 --> 14:56.282
Already left word.

14:56.283 --> 14:57.517
Thanks, Blake. Okay.

14:57.518 --> 14:59.886
- I have to head back in. You're good?
- Okay.

14:59.887 --> 15:02.567
- You just... hang tight, okay?
- Mm-hmm. Yeah.

15:02.822 --> 15:04.057
Is that my blouse?

15:04.058 --> 15:05.557
Looks good.

15:14.767 --> 15:18.169
Well, this is just fantastic.

15:20.339 --> 15:22.508
So, Matt...

15:22.509 --> 15:26.512
