15:59.879 --> 16:01.213
Hmm, sorry, crispy brain.

16:01.214 --> 16:03.349
That's right.

16:03.350 --> 16:04.657
What did you think was happening?

16:04.658 --> 16:05.663
No idea.

16:05.664 --> 16:09.463
I mean, uh, this whole situation
