16:09.464 --> 16:13.392
Deranged gunman outside,
trapped in enclosed space...

16:13.393 --> 16:14.460
Just try to relax.

16:14.461 --> 16:15.527
It's all gonna be fine.

16:15.528 --> 16:17.529
