16:17.530 --> 16:20.532
My heart's racing, my mouth's all dry.

16:20.533 --> 16:22.258
You know, I'll tell you the truth...

16:22.259 --> 16:26.605
when I get this nervous, I
usually smoke a cigarette.

16:26.606 --> 16:28.207
I know, I know, I know.

16:28.208 --> 16:30.242
It's a bad habit, super gross... sue me.

16:30.243 --> 16:31.577
Well, I don't have any cigarettes,

16:31.578 --> 16:33.911
but I do have some gum, if you want.

16:36.381 --> 16:38.649
Yeah, okay.

16:39.251 --> 16:40.285
Thanks.

16:40.286 --> 16:42.019
Yeah.

16:44.938 --> 16:47.040
It's a real love-fest in here.

16:47.041 --> 16:49.775
Stay the course, Jay, stay the course.

16:58.718 --> 17:01.478
You have been to Iraq.

17:03.323 --> 17:05.391
Down! Get down on the ground!

17:05.392 --> 17:06.826
Down!

17:06.827 --> 17:08.060
Get down!

17:08.061 --> 17:09.729
