18:20.767 --> 18:22.768
I was never in Iraq.

18:22.769 --> 18:23.802
Do you understand?

18:23.803 --> 18:27.239
And while I do know who your cousin was,

18:27.240 --> 18:29.408
as to what happened to him...

18:29.409 --> 18:32.611
Safeer, you should have stayed in London.

18:32.612 --> 18:34.112
Instead of killing your own people,

18:34.113 --> 18:36.081
you could be getting your
degree in engineering,

18:36.082 --> 18:38.150
thinking about settling
down with that girl...

18:38.151 --> 18:39.631
what's her name? Fiona.

18:40.385 --> 18:42.688
Oh, yeah.

18:42.689 --> 18:44.122
I know everything about you.

18:44.123 --> 18:46.558
Which is why you're gonna tell me

18:46.559 --> 18:49.628
when and where the next
truck-bomb is set to go off,

18:49.629 --> 18:52.898
so more innocent Muslims
don't have to die...

18:52.899 --> 18:57.002
_

