particularly thorny passage

19:09.615 --> 19:11.616
of the Qasida, by Al-Buhturi.

19:11.617 --> 19:15.287
But we will never speak of
this again, do you understand?

19:15.288 --> 19:16.321
Sorry, Mom?

19:16.322 --> 19:17.722
- Yeah.
- I just talked to Dad.

19:17.723 --> 19:19.457
I just wanted to let
you know, I-I told him

19:19.458 --> 19:21.379
- what's going on.
- Yeah, yeah. No, no, that's great.

19:21.380 --> 19:22.160
- Okay.
- Okay.

19:22.161 --> 19:24.162
All right, baby, I'll
check in with you later.

19:24.944 --> 19:26.432
Okay.

