and of this nation supersede

20:26.204 --> 20:27.771
any personal desires,

20:27.772 --> 20:31.608
and the department needs you in Angola.

20:31.609 --> 20:35.012
You're the only one available
with the necessary experience.

20:35.013 --> 20:37.714
You know what, Miss Tolliver?

20:37.715 --> 20:42.352
