23:02.091 --> 23:04.560
Oh, my God, you gave me pot gum?!

23:04.561 --> 23:06.261
Yes.

23:06.262 --> 23:07.829
Dude, study after study proves

23:07.830 --> 23:09.298
marijuana's efficacy in treating anxiety.

23:09.299 --> 23:11.133
Uh, you should thank me.

23:11.134 --> 23:13.702
I didn't even know pot gum was a thing.

23:15.071 --> 23:17.439
The video... the vid...

23:17.440 --> 23:20.275
If I get caught, I'm so screwed.

23:20.276 --> 23:23.178
Hey, just something to calm you down, man.

23:23.179 --> 23:25.180
Had to... had to calm you down, man.

23:25.181 --> 23:27.282
Oh, you were acting so guilty, so weird.

23:27.283 --> 23:29.651
You were all, mm, being
so straight. It was...

23:33.689 --> 23:35.657
- What are you talking about?
- Wait a minute.

23:35.658 --> 23:37.158
Did you, uh...?

23:37.159 --> 23:40.028
I mean... did you hook...?

23:40.029 --> 23:42.789
Did you hook up with Daisy or something?

23:47.903 --> 23:49.771
She never would never.

23:49.772 --> 23:51.873
- She would never.
- Ah, she... ah, she would.

23:51.874 --> 23:53.942
- Ah, she...
- Wait.

23:53.943 --> 23:55.744
Wait a minute. Did you?

23:55.745 --> 23:57.679
You went back

23:57.680 --> 23:59.114
on your word!

23:59.115 --> 24:01.382
